{"id": 587, "genre": 1001, "title": "一句话证明你患有“找不到东西”病！", "description": "你看到我的手机/手表/眼镜/钥匙/钱包/外套了吗？", "record_count": 3597, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183656PUA2mGJkoY59TtVZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-26T12:36:35Z", "options": [{"id": 20736, "content": "我的镜儿?", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211428cyGPwNuR01sOQSbZ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201854}, {"id": 20225, "content": "妈，你记不记得……", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 210759}, {"id": 21506, "content": "嗯？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278210}, {"id": 44034, "content": "各种找不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440413}, {"id": 20227, "content": "我在外面常找不到自己手机…打给自己“您拨打的电话已关机”???", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269099}, {"id": 20739, "content": "出了门觉得世界模糊一片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272485}, {"id": 20228, "content": "我˘ﻬ˘的˘ﻬ˘衣˘ﻬ˘服˘ﻬ˘呢˘ﻬ˘？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226933}, {"id": 24836, "content": "原来在手上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304094}, {"id": 20229, "content": "我的钥匙呢。工作时，我的脑子呢。吃饭时我的胃口呢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 54876}, {"id": 20485, "content": "我的手机呢？！？（结果手里拿着/在口袋里放着）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270907}, {"id": 20230, "content": "明明买了一打扎头的，可每次梳头，只找到一个。\n明明好几支唇膏，化妆时，也会找不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137854}, {"id": 21767, "content": "谁，能不能给我打个电话，不知道塞那里去了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281379}, {"id": 20232, "content": "好想给各种找不到的东西打个电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267234}, {"id": 20233, "content": "快交出来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134885}, {"id": 20234, "content": "刚买的零食呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258565}, {"id": 21514, "content": "眼镜！！！永远找不到！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277927}, {"id": 20235, "content": "感觉身边有一个小型的黑洞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269460}, {"id": 21259, "content": "银行人，通常会说，我的笔呢，谁拿了我的笔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249548}, {"id": 20236, "content": "“刚才还看见来着，怎么这会儿找不到了？”", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211412rxbnRSjvM85g1kuB.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254951}, {"id": 20237, "content": "卧槽，卧槽，不会又掉了吧！（。慌张摸口袋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257385}, {"id": 20238, "content": "唉 我要找什么来着", "image": null, "praise_count": 228, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493}, {"id": 22286, "content": "“诶诶，那个……哎呀我要说什么来着_(:_」∠)_” 找不到记忆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285610}, {"id": 20239, "content": "不找了不找了，过几天它就出来了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254759}, {"id": 20495, "content": "喂喂喂，你稍等，我手机找不到了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270947}, {"id": 26383, "content": "我刚要说什么？你别打岔，我好好想想。完了，我想不起来了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311407}, {"id": 20240, "content": "过几天就出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268239}, {"id": 21265, "content": "回到家楼下掏掏口袋，钥匙又落在公司了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205367}, {"id": 20242, "content": "我想找什么的呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269509}, {"id": 20498, "content": "找了半天手机最后发现特么就在手上?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270954}, {"id": 22802, "content": "打着电话找手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288567}, {"id": 20243, "content": "我的药呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258675}, {"id": 20499, "content": "我就得我明明放在这的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267626}, {"id": 20244, "content": "它不就在这儿吗，怎么我刚才没看见呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227136}, {"id": 20500, "content": "我记得我明明放在这的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267626}, {"id": 20501, "content": "马丹，我的袜子又被偷了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270963}, {"id": 21781, "content": "你还在卧室找什么？快下来，昨天晚上车钥匙又没拔，晚上跪方便面去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281617}, {"id": 20246, "content": "好想给每件东西都配备手机....", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269538}, {"id": 20503, "content": "突然急着找任何东西时总想给它打个电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92856}, {"id": 21015, "content": "先不找了，明天就出来了。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258694}, {"id": 20760, "content": "我是一条鱼？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194834}, {"id": 20505, "content": "我的眼镜呢？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270958}, {"id": 21017, "content": "东西应该不在家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249558}, {"id": 20506, "content": "知道自己有这个臭毛病，每次收拾东西专门找个好地方细致地放好，尼玛每次坑的都是自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270995}, {"id": 20251, "content": "我刚刚要找什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267058}, {"id": 20252, "content": "怎么找都找不到手机，急得我一甩手，手机都飞出去了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267058}, {"id": 21021, "content": "老婆！你来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267609}, {"id": 20256, "content": "“不可能！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169515}, {"id": 20512, "content": "刚才就放这了！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154051}, {"id": 20257, "content": "不可能，我明明放这了的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250881}, {"id": 20769, "content": "在哪里？在哪里？我刚刚不是放在这里吗？在哪里？哦，在这里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256326}]}